---
import ModuleLayout from '../../layouts/ModuleLayout.astro';
---

<ModuleLayout moduleId="hong" title="洪荒">
  <div class="hong-overview">
    <section class="intro-section">
      <h2>洪荒神怪之录</h2>
      <p>洪荒之时，神魔并起，异兽横行。诸多神兽或为祥瑞，或为凶兆，记载于《山海经》《神异经》等典籍之中。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="features-grid">
      <a href="/hong/divine-beasts" class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🐉</div>
        <h3>神兽录</h3>
        <p>祥瑞神兽图鉴</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/hong/evil-beasts" class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🦄</div>
        <h3>异兽图</h3>
        <p>凶险异兽图鉴</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/hong/birth-match" class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
        <h3>出生匹配</h3>
        <p>神兽缘分测试</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/hong/deity-tree" class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">🌳</div>
        <h3>神灵谱系</h3>
        <p>神系族谱关系</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/hong/auspicious" class="feature-card">
        <div class="card-icon">✨</div>
        <h3>祥瑞凶兆</h3>
        <p>吉凶兽对照</p>
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="beasts-section">
      <h2>著名神兽</h2>
      <div class="beasts-showcase">
        <div class="beast-card">
          <div class="beast-icon">🐉</div>
          <h3>龙</h3>
          <p class="beast-type">神兽</p>
          <p class="beast-desc">鳞虫之长，能幽能明，能细能巨。呼风唤雨，主宰海域。为四大灵兽之首。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="beast-card">
          <div class="beast-icon">🦅</div>
          <h3>凤凰</h3>
          <p class="beast-type">神兽</p>
          <p class="beast-desc">百鸟之王，火之精灵。浴火重生，主宰南方。为祥瑞之兆。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="beast-card">
          <div class="beast-icon">🦒</div>
          <h3>麒麟</h3>
          <p class="beast-type">神兽</p>
          <p class="beast-desc">仁兽也，麋身牛尾鱼鳞。性情温和，不履生虫，不折生草。为祥瑞之兆。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="beast-card">
          <div class="beast-icon">🐢</div>
          <h3>白泽</h3>
          <p class="beast-type">神兽</p>
          <p class="beast-desc">通万物之情，晓鬼神之事。博学多闻，能言人语。为吉祥之兽。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style>
    .hong-overview { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .intro-section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: rgba(240, 96, 64, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(240, 96, 64, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; }
    .intro-section h2 { color: #f06040; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .intro-section p { color: #888; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .feature-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(240, 96, 64, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .feature-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #f06040; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(240, 96, 64, 0.15); }
    .card-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .feature-card h3 { color: #f0e8d8; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; }
    .feature-card p { color: #888; margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .beasts-section h2 { color: #f06040; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .beasts-showcase { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .beast-card { padding: 2rem; background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.8); border: 1px solid rgba(240, 96, 64, 0.2); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .beast-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #f06040; }
    .beast-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .beast-card h3 { color: #f0c080; margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0; }
    .beast-type { color: #f06040; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; }
    .beast-desc { color: #aaa; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</ModuleLayout>
